            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]连续开车8小时后被诊断截瘫！腰椎间盘突出这些一定要注意】50岁的老程患有腰椎间盘突出，春节开车从深圳回老家，来回都是8小时，这趟下来，老程就觉得腰...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>连续开车8小时后被诊断截瘫！腰椎间盘突出这些一定要注意】50岁的老程患有腰椎间盘突出，春节开车从深圳回老家，来回都是8小时，这趟下来，老程就觉得腰不舒服。他像以往一样在腰背部按摩敲打，没想到病情加重，去医院竟被诊断为马尾综合征、截瘫，这是腰椎间盘突出症最严重的情况。医生提醒：程先生腰椎间盘巨大突出、又长途开车久坐，加上不当按摩导致马尾综合征，属于个案。腰椎间盘突出患者日常注意护理，避免高强度运动，避免反复旋转和弯腰，站姿、坐姿要正确，并加强腰背肌训练。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%85%B0%E6%A4%8E%E9%97%B4%E7%9B%98%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BA%E9%95%BF%E9%80%94%E5%BC%80%E8%BD%A6%E5%90%8E%E7%98%AB%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%85%B0%E6%A4%8E%E9%97%B4%E7%9B%98%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BA%E9%95%BF%E9%80%94%E5%BC%80%E8%BD%A6%E5%90%8E%E7%98%AB%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#男子腰椎间盘突出长途开车后瘫了#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4734909600956464" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a>（南方医科大学深圳医院）<br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/713e54f1ly1gz71zg2gnzj20zk0k0tb4.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Po7bts9vlx07TCpg5D6M01041200hfU20E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;trans_finger=1f0da16358befad33323e3a1b7f95fc9&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=4ub7gI97adQ&amp;Expires=1676035965&amp;ssig=NbSf6gB%2Fhi&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/KOMcBoEFlx07TCpfDpvG010412007AMC0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;trans_finger=62b30a3f061b162e421008955c73f536&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=4ub7gI97adQ&amp;Expires=1676035965&amp;ssig=ZyClpgJDc%2B&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/3FnvsO2Nlx07TCpfDSo0010412004LCu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;trans_finger=40a32e8439c5409a63ccf853562a60ef&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=4ub7gI97adQ&amp;Expires=1676035965&amp;ssig=G%2F%2Bc5v1Wf7&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4734909600956464&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
